The data captured in this repository consists of system prompts and tool
definitions sent on the wire by publicly distributed Claude Code binaries
(downloaded from the public npm registry). Reproduction is for research,
analysis, and commentary purposes. Anthropic retains any rights they may
have in the underlying prompt and tool description text; this archive
asserts no copyright over Anthropic's content, only over the organization,
analysis, and methodology applied here.

If Anthropic requests removal of any specific content, contact the
maintainer; we will comply within 48 hours.
